Class ManagedParentQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.yarn.server.resourcemanager.scheduler.capacity.AbstractCSQueue

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CSQueue, Queue, SchedulerQueue<CSQueue>

    public class ManagedParentQueue
extends AbstractManagedParentQueue
    Auto Creation enabled Parent queue. This queue initially does not have any children to start with and all child leaf queues will be auto created. Currently this does not allow other pre-configured leaf or parent queues to co-exist along with auto-created leaf queues. The auto creation is limited to leaf queues currently.
